Just to be clear,

39
00:02:44,799 --> 00:02:46,160
I don't feel like going home right now.

40
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,160
I'm not here

41
00:02:49,359 --> 00:02:50,480
to bring you back home.

42
00:02:50,839 --> 00:02:51,959
Since you get to come out,

43
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,280
let's have fun today.

44
