I like the dog.

54
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,959
Look how pitiful it is

55
00:03:10,119 --> 00:03:10,880
getting crushed by the rabbit.

56
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,480
Save it.

57
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:12,799
All right.

58
00:03:13,079 --> 00:03:14,720
Dog rescue operation begins!

59
