Dad,

66
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,280
I want to eat watermelon.

67
00:03:46,519 --> 00:03:47,760
Come. I'll buy it for you.

68
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,320
I want to eat it too.

69
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:54,320
Wait here.

70
00:04:08,079 --> 00:04:09,280
Eat slowly.

71
00:04:09,519 --> 00:04:11,160
