72
00:04:22,239 --> 00:04:22,920
During the summer holidays

73
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,280
when I was young,

74
00:04:25,559 --> 00:04:26,600
my father would buy me watermelon

75
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,480
when I finished practising Taekwondo.

76
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:30,799
It was frozen and
we sliced it up and ate it.

77
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:32,280
It was so refreshing.

78
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,879
But this summer holiday

79
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,679
will definitely be

80
00:04:39,799 --> 00:04:41,520
the worst summer holiday in my life.

81
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,160
Why?

82
00:04:44,679 --> 00:04:46,040
I haven't reconciled with my father yet.

83
00:04:46,679 --> 00:04:47,679
I've suffered enough

84
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,960
by learning how to draw every day.

85
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,199
I still have to work every day now.

86
00:04:51,319 --> 00:04:51,799
I am so sleepy

87
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,280
that it's hard to keep my eyes open.

88
00:04:54,999 --> 00:04:55,840
Aren't you

89
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,199
able to see Gao Zhan every day?

90
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,400
Yes.

91
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,160
I'm supposed to

92
00:05:00,359 --> 00:05:00,920
feel happy

93
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,040
and motivated

94
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,520
because I can see him every day.

95
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,239
But why can't I

96
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,679
cheer up right now?

97
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:13,999
This should also be

98
00:05:14,239 --> 00:05:15,359
my worst summer holiday.

99
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:16,879
Forget it.

100
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:18,319
Can't you

101
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,600
see Xu Jingjing every day as well?

102
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,080
You even ate, studied

103
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,400
and went to karaoke together.

104
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,720
I lied.

105
00:05:24,119 --> 00:05:25,239
It's because you were always

106
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,640
having fun, eating

107
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,480
and dancing with Gao Zhan.

108
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:31,080
I didn't want to lose to you.

109
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,520
I lied too.

110
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:41,920
It was staged.

111
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,520
Staged?

112
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:46,439
I heard you saying

113
00:05:46,799 --> 00:05:48,319
you were going to eat with Xu Jingjing.

114
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:50,160
I didn't want to lose to you too.

115
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:51,960
The silhouette with the flower

116
00:05:51,999 --> 00:05:53,640
was also staged?

117
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:55,359
Am I amazing?

118
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,759
I'm impressed with myself.

119
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,600
Let me tell you.

120
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,199
That was

121
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,679
an old man and an old woman.

122
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,640
The old woman was
holding a stalk of green onions.

123
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,400
Both of them thought

124
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,720
I wanted to steal the green onions.

125
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,600
You are mad.

126
00:06:12,679 --> 00:06:13,199
Do you think

127
00:06:13,359 --> 00:06:14,199
Xu Jingjing knows about this?

128
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:17,679
I already told her.

129
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,999
What did she say?

130
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,160
I'm sure

131
00:06:22,999 --> 00:06:25,319
she doesn't want to see both of us now.

132
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,119
I don't get it.

133
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,080
Why did she copy my Weibo posts?

134
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,999
Today, I kept

135
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,239
scrolling her Douban.

136
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,480
I could feel that she was confused.

137
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:40,080
I felt that too.

138
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,960
It felt like us previously.

139
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,160
I'm still

140
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,520
in a confused state though.

141
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,600
Xu Jingjing.

142
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,400
Yesterday, I actually wanted to...

143
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,840
What is this?

144
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:16,920
It's nothing.

145
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,840
It's just a normal toy.

146
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,679
Did Gao Zhan give it to you?

147
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,280
Do you know

148
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:31,960
why you think

149
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:32,999
this summer holiday is bad?

150
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,559
Because you didn't have fun with me.

151
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:36,400
It was all because

152
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,400
you didn't contact me.

153
00:07:37,679 --> 00:07:38,759
You neglected me.

154
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,359
I didn't.

155
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,840
You are more focused on another guy.

156
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:41,960
I'll hit you if you continue.

157
00:07:42,119 --> 00:07:43,199
Nice to meet you.

158
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:45,720
What's the meaning of this?

159
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,600
Give-up Virtuoso.

160
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:51,879
We've finally met.

161
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,799
Nice to meet you.

162
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,600
Mayonnaise with Rice.

163
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,640
Jingjing.

164
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,640
I saw a dancing event.

165
00:08:48,079 --> 00:08:49,079
I think it suits you.

166
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,400
(I Sing, You Dance)

167
00:09:08,439 --> 00:09:09,120
Xu Jingjing.

168
00:09:11,439 --> 00:09:12,079
Don't worry.

169
00:09:12,839 --> 00:09:14,120
I will be honest with Xu Jingjing.

170
00:09:14,479 --> 00:09:15,199
You've misunderstood.

171
00:09:15,839 --> 00:09:16,880
I don't blame you.

172
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,360
Xu Jingjing

173
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,199
