174
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,319
Xu Jingjing found out?

175
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,199
She is more worried about

176
00:09:24,479 --> 00:09:25,679
why you didn't reply to her message.

177
00:09:26,479 --> 00:09:27,439
Did Xu Jingjing not

178
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,319
say anything else?

179
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,199
No.

180
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,439
She hopes

181
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,760
you can participate in the event.

182
00:09:33,319 --> 00:09:34,120
I hope so too.

183
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,839
You'll participate, right?

184
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,760
Sorry. I have no time.

185
00:09:38,199 --> 00:09:38,679
Isn't this

186
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:39,959
the opportunity you've been waiting for?

187
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,799
To do what you want.

188
00:09:42,199 --> 00:09:43,240
What I want to do
is do the summer holiday homework.

189
00:09:43,599 --> 00:09:44,559
It's the same

190
00:09:44,719 --> 00:09:45,240
whether you do it or not.

191
00:09:45,479 --> 00:09:45,880
I told you.

192
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,280
I have no time for that.

193
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:48,559
You probably

194
00:09:48,719 --> 00:09:49,799
don't have the courage to be yourself.

195
00:09:53,079 --> 00:09:53,719
Xu Jingjing.

196
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,120
Do you

197
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,160
not like yourself?

198
00:10:00,199 --> 00:10:00,959
I used to be like that.

199
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:02,959
But I realised

200
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,880
accepting myself was a lot easier

201
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,959
than forcing myself.

202
00:10:07,079 --> 00:10:08,400
Do the things you are good at

203
00:10:09,799 --> 00:10:10,959
and you will slowly like who you are.

204
00:10:22,599 --> 00:10:23,760
Do the things you are good at

205
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,520
and you will slowly like who you are.

206
00:10:40,319 --> 00:10:41,280
Alice, The Loneliest Whale.

207
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:43,120
Tell me.

208
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,839
Should I go?

209
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,599
Do you think Alice, The Loneliest Whale,

210
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,479
will be here?

211
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:57,040
She has had no updates for a long time.

212
00:10:57,199 --> 00:10:58,120
Did she quit?

213
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,799
No way.

214
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,160
I came here just for her.

215
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:04,920
Exactly.

216
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:06,280
She hasn't

217
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,520
replied to your message yet?

218
00:11:09,199 --> 00:11:10,160
I didn't even go to work today

219
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,199
just to come here and cheer for her.

220
00:11:13,079 --> 00:11:13,559
The event

221
00:11:13,719 --> 00:11:14,920
will end soon.

222
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,679
She won't be coming, right?

223
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:17,839
It's all your fault!

224
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:18,719
I'm sure

225
00:11:18,959 --> 00:11:20,160
you angered her yesterday.

226
00:11:20,439 --> 00:11:21,439
You told me she didn't reply

227
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,479
to your messages

228
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,719
so I went to ask her in person.

229
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,240
I was trying to motivate her.

230
00:11:25,479 --> 00:11:26,559
Motivate her?

231
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:27,199
Didn't you say

232
00:11:27,439 --> 00:11:27,920
she doesn't want

233
00:11:28,079 --> 00:11:28,920
to see us both?

234
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,679
You still told her we are here.

235
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:31,880
It will be a miracle for her to be here.

236
00:11:32,079 --> 00:11:33,199
How can you blame me for that?

237
00:11:33,319 --> 00:11:34,479
I did it out of kindness.

238
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:35,439
Xu Jingjing.

239
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:36,280
You...

240
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,559
Kang Jiawei.

241
00:11:38,199 --> 00:11:39,000
Jingjing.

242
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,439
I knew you would come.

243
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:42,640
Xu Jingjing.

244
00:11:43,479 --> 00:11:44,479
I have something

245
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:46,160
to tell you alone.

246
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:47,599
Is that possible?

247
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:50,559
I am here

248
00:11:52,199 --> 00:11:53,679
to apologise to you.

249
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,319
Kang Jiawei said

250
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,040
you knew about that thing.

251
00:11:59,599 --> 00:12:00,280
Sorry.

252
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,240
Jingjing.

253
00:12:01,439 --> 00:12:02,000
This is not the time

254
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,160
to talk about that.

255
00:12:03,479 --> 00:12:04,040
Right now,

256
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,280
you should prepare for the dance.

257
00:12:05,719 --> 00:12:06,479
I'm really not angry.

258
00:12:06,959 --> 00:12:08,040
I'm not here to dance.

259
00:12:08,319 --> 00:12:09,719
I'm here to apologise to you.

260
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,280
Actually, I wanted to cancel

261
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:12,160
the account

262
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,360
but there are many things

263
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,599
I want to keep.

264
00:12:15,719 --> 00:12:17,719
Also, I'm returning this to you.

265
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,799
You came to find me

266
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,520
just to say that?

267
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,199
Xu Jingjing.

268
00:12:27,599 --> 00:12:28,640
Think about it.

269
00:12:28,959 --> 00:12:30,079
Will you regret it

270
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,520
if you miss this opportunity?

271
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,160
I want to dance

272
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,160
but I don't think I'm good enough.

273
00:12:36,479 --> 00:12:37,559
Why do you think that?

274
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:38,479
Look. Many of them

275
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:39,760
are your fans.

276
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,000
I also heard them

277
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:41,760
talking about you.

278
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,280
They are looking forward to seeing you.

279
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:45,000
But they don't know

280
00:12:45,199 --> 00:12:46,079
that I'm a fake

281
00:12:46,288 --> 00:12:46,888
and a thief.

282
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:48,000
You are not.

283
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:49,559
I don't care.

284
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:51,479
I don't care about the Douban incident.

285
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:52,400
On the contrary,

286
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,760
if you don't dance because of this,

287
00:12:53,959 --> 00:12:55,199
it'll be my biggest regret.

288
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:10,920
So cool.

289
00:13:12,959 --> 00:13:14,280
Are you done talking?

290
00:13:15,199 --> 00:13:16,520
The event is ending soon.

291
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:19,719
