628
00:27:49,439 --> 00:27:50,120
Aren't you getting

629
00:27:50,279 --> 00:27:50,959
a new deskmate too?

630
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:52,239
I will go to science class

631
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,600
and annoy you often.

632
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,679
I welcome you to come and annoy me.

633
00:27:59,080 --> 00:28:00,640
It's late. Go home.

634
00:28:00,959 --> 00:28:01,880
There's class tomorrow.

635
00:28:04,759 --> 00:28:05,719
Kang Jiawei.

636
00:28:09,999 --> 00:28:10,600
Thank you.

637
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,759
For that dog?

638
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,999
I got it after a few tries.

639
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:18,959
No need to thank me.

640
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:32,080
Who told you that you are not the lead?

641
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:34,640
Xu Jingjing, you are the lead.

642
00:28:35,479 --> 00:28:36,640
You drew Pipi well.

643
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:38,439
You are great at Taekwondo.

644
00:28:39,719 --> 00:28:40,640
You are witty, humorous,

645
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:41,840
kind and brave.

646
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:45,800
You are not ordinary at all.

647
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:47,600
Why do you have to care

648
00:28:47,759 --> 00:28:48,719
about what people think of you?

649
00:28:53,679 --> 00:28:54,600
Xu Jingjing, remember.

650
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:56,640
You will forever be

651
00:28:56,840 --> 00:28:58,479
the real lead character

652
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:00,400
under the spotlight of your life.

653
00:29:07,080 --> 00:29:07,840
Thank you

654
00:29:08,959 --> 00:29:10,400
for making me into a better self.

655
00:29:14,279 --> 00:29:15,039
Thank you

656
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:17,400
