But you have to promise me

658
00:29:23,479 --> 00:29:24,800
not to forget about me

659
00:29:26,199 --> 00:29:27,360
after you have a new deskmate.

660
00:29:29,439 --> 00:29:30,519
I won't forget you.

661
00:29:33,600 --> 00:29:34,360
I can't hear you.

662
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:41,519
Kang Jiawei will never forget

663
00:29:41,719 --> 00:29:44,479
Xu Jingjing!

664
00:29:45,840 --> 00:29:47,519
Xu Jingjing will always be

665
00:29:47,679 --> 00:29:50,479
Kang Jiawei's best friend!

666
00:30:12,039 --> 00:30:13,320
Seems like my holiday

667
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:14,759
