672
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,080
No. Well...

673
00:30:50,959 --> 00:30:52,479
Breakfast is ready. Come and eat.

674
00:30:53,239 --> 00:30:54,120
Okay.

675
00:30:59,759 --> 00:31:01,239
Xu.

676
00:31:01,439 --> 00:31:01,999
Hurry.

677
00:31:02,199 --> 00:31:03,080
Pack Jingjing's breakfast.

678
00:31:03,719 --> 00:31:04,959
