680
00:31:06,199 --> 00:31:06,719
Hurry up.

681
00:31:06,999 --> 00:31:08,519
Of course, she has to draw.

682
00:31:08,519 --> 00:31:09,439
After all, we are paying an expensive

683
00:31:09,439 --> 00:31:09,800
drawing course fee.

684
00:31:16,439 --> 00:31:17,320
Mom, I'm not eating.

685
00:31:17,519 --> 00:31:18,199
I'm going out to eat.

686
00:31:18,479 --> 00:31:19,160
Jingjing.

687
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:19,759
Oh.

688
00:31:20,320 --> 00:31:21,360
I received my pay two days ago.

689
00:31:21,719 --> 00:31:23,279
I already transferred the money to you.

690
00:31:23,439 --> 00:31:23,840
Check your account

691
00:31:24,080 --> 00:31:24,880
when you are free.

692
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:27,640
Also, thank you

693
00:31:27,999 --> 00:31:29,279
for paying my fees for me.

694
00:31:29,479 --> 00:31:30,199
I'll pay the rest

695
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:32,080
after I earn them.

696
00:31:32,959 --> 00:31:33,840
Is that good enough?

697
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:34,999
Jingjing.

698
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,120
Jingjing.

699
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:39,679
I didn't ask her

700
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:40,439
for the money.

701
00:31:40,759 --> 00:31:41,800
Enough. Just shut up.

