00:31:43,650 --> 00:31:46,410
(Yuming Senior High School)

703
00:31:52,560 --> 00:31:53,199
Jingjing.

704
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:54,519
Are you looking for me?

705
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:55,479
I need to

706
00:31:55,719 --> 00:31:56,959
ask you for a favour.

707
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:57,880
Sure.

708
00:31:58,600 --> 00:31:59,320
There's a crack

709
00:31:59,719 --> 00:32:00,880
on the helmet

710
00:32:01,120 --> 00:32:02,320
