711
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:03,439
I want you

712
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:05,239
to help me fix it.

713
00:32:06,360 --> 00:32:07,160
Didn't you already decide

714
00:32:07,320 --> 00:32:08,120
not to wear this anymore?

715
00:32:09,719 --> 00:32:10,400
But

716
00:32:10,719 --> 00:32:11,439
I think this helmet

717
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:12,840
means a lot to me.

718
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,880
I want to give it to Huanhuan.

719
00:32:16,320 --> 00:32:16,999
I see.

720
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,039
When I fix it,

721
00:32:18,279 --> 00:32:19,400
let's visit Huanhuan together.

722
00:32:19,679 --> 00:32:20,400
Sure.

723
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,959
Actually, I kept thinking about Huanhuan

724
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:24,600
since we last met.

725
00:32:25,039 --> 00:32:26,519
I think it's tough for Mr. Zhang.

726
00:32:27,120 --> 00:32:28,640
I want to do something for him.

727
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:30,439
It's quite good

728
00:32:30,719 --> 00:32:31,560
to give this to Huanhuan.

729
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,239
Both of you are quite free.

730
00:32:34,959 --> 00:32:35,479
What are you planning

731
00:32:35,679 --> 00:32:36,560
on the first day of school?

732
00:32:37,759 --> 00:32:38,840
Miss Chen.

733
00:32:39,519 --> 00:32:40,400
What?

734
00:32:42,999 --> 00:32:43,840
I'll keep anything

735
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:44,840
unrelated to class.

736
00:32:45,039 --> 00:32:45,560
No.

737
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:46,640
Listen to me.

738
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:55,880
Are you telling the truth?

739
00:32:56,239 --> 00:32:56,719
Yes.

740
00:32:56,999 --> 00:32:58,400
You can ask Kang Jiawei
if you don't believe us.

741
00:32:58,640 --> 00:32:59,120
He met

742
00:32:59,320 --> 00:33:00,160
Mr. Zhang with us.

743
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:05,679
How did that happen?

744
00:33:06,279 --> 00:33:07,880
Miss Chen,

745
00:33:08,479 --> 00:33:10,679
can you not confiscate this helmet

746
00:33:10,679 --> 00:33:12,160
and let me fix it?

747
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,160
I approve.

748
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:14,199
However,

749
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:16,039
don't think about anything

750
00:33:16,239 --> 00:33:17,239
unrelated to class.

751
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:18,759
Definitely!

752
00:33:18,959 --> 00:33:19,560
Thank you, Miss Chen.

753
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:20,560
Thank you, Miss Chen.

