00:33:36,719 --> 00:33:37,519
I didn't know Miss Tian

758
00:33:37,759 --> 00:33:38,320
arranged for us

759
00:33:38,519 --> 00:33:39,400
to sit beside each other.

760
00:33:39,982 --> 00:33:40,982
If you don't want that,

761
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:41,800
I can talk to her

