00:33:49,690 --> 00:33:52,770
(Student On Duty, Chen Yan)

766
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:55,080
Jingjing.

767
00:34:00,120 --> 00:34:01,239
I'm sitting here?

768
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:02,080
Yes.

769
00:34:02,538 --> 00:34:03,360
I told Miss Chen

770
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:04,439
that I want to sit beside you.

771
00:34:04,959 --> 00:34:05,479
After Kang Jiawei left,

772
00:34:05,679 --> 00:34:06,800
I can keep tutoring you.

773
00:34:10,039 --> 00:34:10,880
Keep quiet.

