00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,159
Before class, I want to announce

775
00:34:14,599 --> 00:34:16,079
the coming-of-age ceremony

776
00:34:16,240 --> 00:34:16,760
for all 12th Grade students

777
00:34:16,999 --> 00:34:18,400
that's happening two days later.

778
00:34:18,639 --> 00:34:19,439
All of you and your parents

779
00:34:19,680 --> 00:34:20,360
have to attend the ceremony.

780
00:34:20,559 --> 00:34:21,479
I think

781
00:34:21,680 --> 00:34:22,079
this is

782
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,280
a very important ceremony.

783
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,959
You can understand

784
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:26,639
the responsibility you are shouldering

785
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,400
and your rights.

786
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:29,519
So, I hope

787
00:34:29,720 --> 00:34:31,119
everyone can use this opportunity

788
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:33,039
to prepare
what you want to say to your parents

789
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:33,680
and prepare

790
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,519
the coming-of-age present
for your classmates.

791
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:36,479
Let's begin

792
00:34:36,680 --> 00:34:37,639
your 12th Grade journey

793
00:34:38,039 --> 00:34:40,200
through an exchange with
your parents and your friends.

