00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,880
How do you feel when you see this?

795
00:34:52,439 --> 00:34:53,800
Are you thinking of that song?

796
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,639
Where has the time gone?

797
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:57,760
All Grade 12th students.

798
00:34:59,159 --> 00:35:00,439
For all of you,

799
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,959
the college entrance examination

800
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:04,040
is near

801
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,360
and imminent.

802
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,079
What do

803
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,119
281 days mean?

