00:35:08,439 --> 00:35:08,920
It means

805
00:35:09,119 --> 00:35:10,959
281 times of pushing forward.

806
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:13,320
It means 281 times

807
00:35:13,519 --> 00:35:14,680
working hard.

808
00:35:15,680 --> 00:35:17,039
So, from now on,

809
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:19,039
every one of you
has to pull yourself together

810
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:21,240
and treat every exam

811
00:35:21,559 --> 00:35:22,639
and every minute seriously.

812
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,439
Do you understand?

813
00:35:24,680 --> 00:35:25,519
Yes.

814
00:35:26,039 --> 00:35:26,720
Louder.

815
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:28,400
Yes!

816
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,479
Let's begin your exam.

817
00:35:34,730 --> 00:35:35,980
(Lu Xun)

818
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:42,599
Over here!

819
00:35:44,999 --> 00:35:46,800
Ace students.

820
00:35:47,079 --> 00:35:47,880
How did you do in your exams?

821
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:50,200
Don't mention it.

822
00:35:50,599 --> 00:35:51,439
I think

823
00:35:51,687 --> 00:35:52,486
I screwed up badly.

824
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,519
Come on.

825
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:54,639
You said the same thing

