00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:55,519
during the last exam.

827
00:35:56,039 --> 00:35:57,200
I'm telling the truth.

828
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,439
I was only working and drawing

829
00:35:58,680 --> 00:35:59,159
during the holidays.

830
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,039
I didn't even arrange

831
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,079
a schedule to study.

832
00:36:01,559 --> 00:36:02,519
I have a feeling

833
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:04,240
that it's over for me.

834
00:36:05,439 --> 00:36:06,240
Enough talk about this.

835
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:07,439
Let's talk about something happy.

836
00:36:07,999 --> 00:36:09,039
Which of your family members

837
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,320
will be coming
to the coming-of-age ceremony?

838
00:36:11,079 --> 00:36:12,240
Everyone from my family
says they are coming.

839
00:36:12,479 --> 00:36:13,200
My parents

840
00:36:13,439 --> 00:36:13,999
and my grandparents.

841
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:15,079
Dream on.

842
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:15,720
The school

843
00:36:15,959 --> 00:36:16,959
only allows one parent to attend.

844
00:36:17,559 --> 00:36:18,639
My family...

845
00:36:19,479 --> 00:36:20,599
I think it should be my mother.

846
00:36:21,559 --> 00:36:22,840
My relationship with my dad
is still bad.

847
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,039
It's still bad

848
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,079
after the summer holidays?

849
00:36:26,599 --> 00:36:28,360
If he wants to cause problems for me,

850
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:30,360
I'll entertain him all day long.

851
00:36:30,959 --> 00:36:31,840
Don't be angry.

852
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:34,439
What present do you want
for the ceremony?

853
00:36:34,639 --> 00:36:35,280
I'll buy it for you.

854
00:36:35,559 --> 00:36:36,320
An expensive one!

855
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:38,720
I'll give you another chance.

856
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,280
Say it again.

857
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:43,200
Actually, I don't want anything.

858
00:36:43,519 --> 00:36:43,999
I just want to

859
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:45,400
