870
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:12,280
You're so uncultured.

871
00:37:14,639 --> 00:37:15,999
Will you admit

872
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:18,439
that our Jingjing is talented?

873
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,760
With her skills, she has already

874
00:37:21,039 --> 00:37:21,959
reached this level

875
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:22,800
after two months.

876
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:24,559
She's a genius.

877
00:37:26,439 --> 00:37:27,639
Our money didn't go to waste.

878
00:37:32,079 --> 00:37:33,639
Will it kill you to admit it?

879
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:35,559
Did she really draw this?

